<span id="freeTextContainer13342125278065919212">To be honest I did not finish this book. The beginning was great right up until the main character changes from a man into a beast. Right after that he mates with two lioness and that was a little too much of a beast for me to like. I skipped ahead a bit(something that I never do) and it didn&apos;t seem to get any better. I skipped to the end to see if I should finish it and in a matter of a couple sentences the beast turns back into a man because of Belle&apos;s love and that is how it ends. Not an endi</span>
